<ContentSlide Title="Reactive Programming">
    <p>
        <b>Imperative Programming</b>
        <ul>
            <li>Statements executed one after another</li>
            <li>Assignments have no impact on already executed computations</li>
        </ul>

        <CodeBox>
            var b = 1
            var c = 2
            var a = b + c
            b = 10
            console.log(a) // 3
        </CodeBox>
    </p>

    <p>
        <b>Reactive Programming</b>
        <ul>
            <li>Computations are dynamic, they automatically update as dependencies change</li>
        </ul>

        <CodeBox>
            var b = 1
            var c = 2
            var a $= b + c   // let $= be a special "reactive operator"
            b = 10
            console.log(a) // 12
        </CodeBox>
    </p>
</ContentSlide>